// ============================================================
// Test: include_python.ncs
// Purpose: External Python command via Include.
//   - Register python_echo.py as external command
//   - Call it with arguments via Bash
// ============================================================

// -- Step 1: Register echo tool as external command --
// exec=default uses the script's shebang (#!/usr/bin/env python3)
!@Include ./tests/data/python_echo.py alias=echop

// -- Step 2: Call the external echo tool with arguments --
!@echop Hello from NCS via Include Python!
